---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import SectionHeading from "@/components/SectionHeading.astro";
---
<Layout
  title="Tournamental for creators &amp; influencers"
  description="Sports creators and prediction influencers get a verifiable record, a branded syndicate, a global audience, and a revenue share — for free."
  ogImage="/og/influencers.png"
>
  <section class="container-page pt-16 pb-12">
    <SectionHeading
      eyebrow="For creators &amp; influencers"
      title="Your record is your brand. Make it provable."
      lede="Tournamental turns every prediction you make into a signed, public receipt — and gives you a branded space to bring your audience along for the ride."
    />
  </section>

  <section class="container-page pb-12">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Verifiable record</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-200 mt-2">Every prediction is timestamped before kickoff and signed. Quote your VStamp ledger anywhere. Prove your accuracy across years, tournaments, and platforms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Your own syndicate</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-200 mt-2">A branded path at <code>play.tournamental.com/s/yourname</code>. Your audience joins your leaderboard, your tagline lives on every share card, your colours on every digest.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Revenue share</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-200 mt-2">Affiliate-router placement on tournament-relevant sportsbook offers. Auto-generated short-form clips you can post directly. Bonus tokens for every referral that activates.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Auto-clip pipeline</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-200 mt-2">Every key moment in every match becomes a 6-10s vertical clip with your handle and your call overlay. We post to your TikTok, Instagram, X, and YouTube Shorts on your behalf.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Audience tools</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-200 mt-2">CSV-import your existing list. One-click invite via Telegram and WhatsApp. Bulk-tag the top 100 fans for early-access tokens during big tournaments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">No exclusivity</h3>
        <p class="text-ink-200 mt-2">Run on whatever channels you already own. We're the back-end and the leaderboard, not your jailer.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-prose pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">How the revenue share works</h2>
    <p class="prose-vt">Every paid integration on the platform — sportsbook affiliate clickouts, sponsored tournament placements, ad-funded clip distribution — passes through a transparent revenue split. Open-source contributors get a slice via the <strong>Drips Network</strong>. Influencers driving meaningful activity in their syndicate get a slice via the <strong>partner program</strong>. The split formula is in the open-source <a href="/open-source" class="link">repo</a>; nobody has to trust us.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-10">What we ask in return</h2>
    <ul class="prose-vt list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>Your real predictions, signed before kickoff. No retro edits, ever.</li>
      <li>Honest disclosure on any sponsored content (we have a banner template).</li>
      <li>A working email or Telegram so we can ping you on payout days.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="prose-vt mt-8">
      Want in early?
      <a href="mailto:partners@tournamental.com" class="link">partners@tournamental.com</a>
      — say what you cover and roughly how big your audience is. We're keeping the partner program tight while we land the World Cup, then opening it broadly.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
